order-style: none; width: 672px;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817111935_80590.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817112454_75359.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">D8 / 阿尔苏阿 – 佩德罗索 Pedrouzo徒步</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">徒步距离：21公里 &nbsp; &nbsp;穿越小村镇：Santa Irene； &nbsp; 夜宿佩德罗索 &nbsp; 难度系数：中； 途中风光：原始森林、乡间小路、小村庄</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817112946_96069.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">D9 / 佩德罗索 Pedrouzo-Arca – 圣地亚哥 徒步</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">徒步距离：19公里 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 穿越小村镇：Monte do Gozo &nbsp;难度系数：中； &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 途中风光：山林、小村庄、古城圣地亚哥</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">到达圣城---圣地亚哥.德.孔波斯特拉，和其他朝圣者一样，来到圣地亚哥大教堂前席地而坐，抬头瞻仰这座神圣的大教堂。之后走进教堂，把自己当成一个真正的朝圣者，向伟大的圣人圣地亚哥致以最虔诚的膜拜。带上朝圣护照，到朝圣证书办公室领取朝圣者证书。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">入住圣地亚哥酒店。</p><p><br/></p>', '短途', 1, '2017-09-01', '2017-09-02', 230, '青城山目的地', '青城山景点', '活动内容你说了算', '2017-09-01 12:12:12', '火车站集合地点', 2, '火车', 34, 0, '18328402805', '张翠翠领队', '1504324081.jpg#1504324083.jpg#1504324085.jpeg#1504324088.jpg#1504324090.jpg', '2017-09-02 08:13:01'),
(5, '长春一日游', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px;\">路线：</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px;\">北京——马德里——莱昂——阿斯托加Astorga——蓬费拉达Ponferrada——俄塞布里尔O Cebreiro——撒利亚Sarria——波特马林Portomarin——帕拉斯德雷Palas de Rei——阿尔苏阿Arzua——佩德罗索 Pedrouzo——圣地亚哥——波尔图——里斯本——辛特拉——罗卡角——里斯本——北京。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817141153_67681.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"392\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">D1 / 北京 -- &nbsp;马德里 &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;（航班待定）到达后， 我们前往入住酒店休息。 机上餐。 &nbsp; &nbsp;/&nbsp;&nbsp; 住宿：马德里</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">D2 / 马德里 &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">‘阳光优雅地漫步旅店的草坪，人鱼在石刻墙壁弹奏着竖琴’—《马德里不思议》。古老而繁华的格兰维亚大街、充满艺术气息的马约尔广场、大教堂，赖着阳光端着红色桑格利亚汽酒的人们，马德里的每一处角落都透着霸气的旧日辉煌和优雅的现代慷懒，就让我们从马德里不思议开始我们的旅行吧；其他亮点：太阳门、西班牙广场、大地女神喷泉、邮政大楼、阿尔卡拉门、西班牙最大的斗牛场、阿多查火车站。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">徒步距离：城市休闲游，约12km。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">马德里·大地女神喷泉</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170816/20170816142629_30043.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px;\">马德里·太阳门广场</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817150011_58766.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"440\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817112108_95013.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817112210_61794.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817112109_68059.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">D3 / 马德里 - 莱昂 335KM &nbsp;行车&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">莱昂，一个已经在世界上消逝的王国，最初成立是作为罗马军第七军团的营地，后来发展成为中世纪一个王国的首都。莱昂辉煌的历史给人类留下了丰富的文化遗产，他也是朝圣之路必经之路。莱昂的重要建筑有：莱昂大教堂、圣依希德罗教堂和圣马哥修道院。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">拥有700多年历史的莱昂大教堂*，其高耸入云的塔尖和拱璧，以及惊人的内部设计代表着城市的精神中心。大教堂作为西班牙首屈一指的哥特式杰作，其内部却弥漫着柔美的光彩，明亮的玫瑰花彩窗和镶满彩色玻璃窗的走廊，是教堂最美丽最壮观的特色。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">圣依希德罗教堂最早可追溯到1063年。其中的万神殿安放着20多位君主的遗体，然而19世纪初不幸被拿破仑军队洗劫一空。教堂的主体融合了多种风格，但正门的大门采用了纯粹的罗马式风格，教堂内部的彩绘是值得观赏的亮点。圣马可修道院是西班牙文艺复兴时期的典型代表，最初是12世纪为去圣地亚哥的朝圣者提供住宿而建的修道院，之后改建为圣地亚哥骑士军总部，现已改建为国营古堡酒店。其它知名景点：西班牙天才建筑师高迪设计的新哥特式风格的伯提内之家，Palacio de Los Guzmanes宫殿，马约尔广场。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">徒步距离：城市休闲游，约11km。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 30px;\">莱昂·莱昂大教堂</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817160752_15815.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"453\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817111018_58783.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">D4 / 莱昂 – 阿斯托加Astorga 51KM – 蓬费拉达Ponferrada 62KM –俄塞布里尔O Cebreiro 53KM – 撒利亚Sarria 45KM &nbsp;行车</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">阿斯托加，这座古城曾是银路（Via de la plata）上战略地位很重要的要塞，银路是一条古罗马公路，贯穿安达卢西亚和西班牙西北部，后来阿斯托加又成为圣地亚哥朝圣路上的一座重要驿站。城中高高耸立的是两座纪念性建筑---大教堂和主教宫（外观）。值得一提的是这座神话般的由形态各异的小塔楼组成的主教宫，是由天才建筑设计师高迪设计。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">蓬费拉达，这个城市的名字来源于一座为朝圣者建立的桥的名字，蓬费拉达雄伟的城堡是圣殿骑士于12-14世纪间建立，目的是保护圣地朝圣者。在中世纪，这里曾是西班牙西北部最大的堡垒之一。我们将在城堡脚下的餐厅品尝当地特色：猪蹄煲。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">俄塞布里尔依山而建，已从属加里西亚省，与里昂接壤。俄镇是朝圣之路上最不同寻常的一个村镇，圣经载：1300年，建于9世纪的教堂见证了一场奇迹，这里的葡萄酒流成了鲜血的河流，面包变成了肉。这里还保留了很多朝圣者寄宿过的盖着茅草顶的石屋，是典型的古凯尔特风格。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">撒利亚是我们朝圣之路徒步旅行的起点，到达撒利亚后，我们到Iglesia santa marina教堂取得护照。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;\" href=\"http://undefined\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">阿斯托加·阿斯托加古堡</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170816/20170816144052_46358.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"483\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\">这已经是私人滴啦~</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px;\">蓬费拉达Ponferrada教堂城堡</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817155047_11894.jpeg\" width=\"600\" height=\"318\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817111736_38929.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817111736_48908.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817112257_81979.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">D5 / 撒利亚 – 波特马林Portomarin 徒步</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">徒步距离：22.5公里，海拔上升395km。 &nbsp; 穿越小村镇：Barbadelo,Ferreiros</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">难度系数：中； &nbsp; &nbsp;途中风光：栎树林、乡间小道、广阔山野、河流、村庄； &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817112715_49822.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817112108_95875.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170816/20170816144248_70204.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">开拔！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">D6 / 波特马林 – 帕拉斯德雷Palas de Rei &nbsp;徒步</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">徒步距离：25公里； &nbsp; &nbsp;穿越小村镇：Gonzar, O Hospital da Cruz, Ligonde</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">难度系数：中； &nbsp; &nbsp;途中风光：山峦、小牧场、村子、公路； &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170816/20170816150215_50569.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"393\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817111848_74416.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817111848_13240.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">D7 / 帕拉斯德雷 – 阿尔苏阿Arzua &nbsp;徒步&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">徒步距离：29公里； &nbsp; &nbsp; 穿越小村镇：Mato-Casanova, Melide, Ribadiso； &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;夜宿阿尔苏阿</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">难度系数：高； &nbsp; &nbsp;途中风光：森林、中世纪古村落Ribadiso、小河、古桥Puente La Reina</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170816/20170816150249_97542.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"384\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817111935_15937.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817111935_80590.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817112454_75359.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">D8 / 阿尔苏阿 – 佩德罗索 Pedrouzo徒步</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">徒步距离：21公里 &nbsp; &nbsp;穿越小村镇：Santa Irene； &nbsp; 夜宿佩德罗索 &nbsp; 难度系数：中； 途中风光：原始森林、乡间小路、小村庄</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170817/20170817112946_96069.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">D9 / 佩德罗索 Pedrouzo-Arca – 圣地亚哥 徒步</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">徒步距离：19公里 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 穿越小村镇：Monte do Gozo &nbsp;难度系数：中； &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 途中风光：山林、小村庄、古城圣地亚哥</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">到达圣城---圣地亚哥.德.孔波斯特拉，和其他朝圣者一样，来到圣地亚哥大教堂前席地而坐，抬头瞻仰这座神圣的大教堂。之后走进教堂，把自己当成一个真正的朝圣者，向伟大的圣人圣地亚哥致以最虔诚的膜拜。带上朝圣护照，到朝圣证书办公室领取朝圣者证书。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">入住圣地亚哥酒店。</p><p><br/></p>', '自驾游', 3, '2017-09-01', '2017-09-02', 230, '长春目的地', '长春景点', '活动内容你说了算长春', '2017-09-01 12:12:12', '火车站集合地点', 2, '火车', 34, 0, '18328402805', '张翠翠领队', '1504328685.jpg#1504328688.jpg#1504328690.jpg#1504328692.jpg#1504328694.jpg#1504328700.jpg#1504328704.jpg', '2017-09-02 05:06:47');

